      19 failures across 5 classes — CitationExtractorTests (8), PrivilegeLeakageTests (7),
      ConfidenceScoringServiceTests (2), VerifyCitationsTests (1), CitationVerificationServiceTests (1).
      All fall within existing relevant-files glob `Services/Ai/Safety/*.cs` — no scope change,
      annotation only. See `notes/handoffs/phase23-scope-delta-2026-05-31.md`.
    </scope-extension>
