      no factory edits (§4.5 ✓); 0 `Failed` traits (§4.3 ✓); class-level `repaired` traits on all
      5 files (§6.2 ✓). Build clean (0 errors / 17 pre-existing warnings).
    </completion-note>
  </notes>
</task>
